.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-CHANNEL-GRAPH" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-channel-graph \- list channels from the gossip graph
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-channel-graph
.RB [ --limit
.IR N ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Returns channels visible in the local gossip graph via
.BR listchannels .
Default limit is 100.
.PP
Output:
.nf
[{source, destination, short_channel_id, satoshis, active}]
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-node-gossip (1),
.BR lightning-route-find (1)
